name: PARIS
description:
A magical city creates a magical watch.


Fashion is a core part of the Parisian lifestyle, no matter if the apparel is prêt-à-porter or haute couture the look is effortless yet full of details.


Ultra-thin 7mm Case
Surgical Grade Stainless Steel
Scratch Resistant Sapphire Glass
Italian Calfskin strap with Butterfly clasp
Water Resistant to minimum 5 ATM (50m)
Now including a free extended warranty


Delivered in a handmade piano lacquered wooden box with certificate, polishing cloth and owners manual.
